      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/gold-climbs-to-record-as-momentum-builds-on-rate-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在对美联储转向和地缘政治风险的猜测支撑金价上涨后，金价跃升至历史新高。]]></description>
